book:
KTaglib

 &reftitle.intro;


   The module enables you to read and write ID3v1, ID3v2 and Ogg tags.
   It is build using the taglib extension from the KDE project.




    At the moment ktaglib is able to read and write ID3v1 and ID3v2 tags.



